<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Under Maintenance | ToyBerry</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF5F5 0%, #FFFDF0 100%);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }
    .background-shapes div {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.08);
      animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .shape-1 { width: 300px; height: 300px; top: -100px; left: -100px; animation-delay: 0s; }
    .shape-2 { width: 250px; height: 250px; bottom: -80px; right: -80px; animation-delay: 2s; background: rgba(255, 230, 109, 0.15) !important; }
    .shape-3 { width: 150px; height: 150px; top: 40%; right: 10%; animation-delay: 4s; background: rgba(78, 205, 196, 0.1) !important; }
    
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-20px) scale(1.05); }
    }
    
    .maintenance-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      border-radius: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      padding: 50px 40px;
      max-width: 580px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      z-index: 10;
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    
    .toy-icon {
      font-size: 5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #FF6B6B, #FFB81C);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      animation: spin-slow 12s linear infinite;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    @keyframes spin-slow {
      0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #2D3436;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="background-shapes">
    <div class="shape-1"></div>
    <div class="shape-2"></div>
    <div class="shape-3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center px-3">
    <div class="maintenance-card">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <i class="bi bi-gear-fill toy-icon"></i>
      </div>
      
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3">
        <img src="/uploads/toyberry.jpg" alt="ToyBerry Logo" class="me-2 rounded-3" style="width: 42px; height: 42px; object-fit: contain; border: 1.5px solid #FF6B6B;">
        <h2 class="brand-title m-0">ToyBerry</h2>
      </div>

      <h3 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3">Under Scheduled Maintenance</h3>
      <p class="text-muted fs-6 lh-lg mb-4">
        We are busy adding new premium toys and polishing our e-commerce shelf to give you an even better experience. We will be back online shortly!
      </p>

      <div class="border-top pt-4 mt-2">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-4 text-muted small">
          <span><i class="bi bi-clock me-1 text-primary"></i> Est. Time: ~30 Mins</span>
          <span><i class="bi bi-whatsapp me-1 text-success"></i> WhatsApp Support</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
